  "text": "For Western blot analysis, cells were lysed in Triton X-100 lysis buffer and separated by SDS-PAGE as described. [CITATION_1] Proteins were detected using antibodies against COX-2 (Santa Cruz Biotechnology, Santa Cruz, Calif) and ␤-actin (Sigma). The CYP2C9 antibody used was purified by Eurogenetec (Seraing, Belgium) from rabbits immunized with a CYP2C9 peptide (RRRKLPPGPTPLPIC).",
